OL,7,FOnce a term, 60 medical students from
OL,8,FImperial College London gather in a
OL,9,Flarge room at Charing Cross Hospital to
OL,10,Fattend the scene of a cardiac arrest.
OL,11,FThere's blood ` lots of it ` and a
OL,12,Fbedside nurse performing chest
OL,13,Fcompressions.
OL,15,FOne doctor is furiously taking notes,
OL,16,Fwhile another is standing anxiously
OL,17,Fover the heart rate monitor.
OL,19,F"What should we do next?" they ask the
OL,20,Fmedical students.
OL,3,CHow one university is using VR to teach
OL,4,Cmedical students how to deal with
OL,5,Ccardiac arrests
